11 BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES OF THE 1ST SESSION OF
12 THE 60TH OKLAHOMA LEGISLATURE, THE SENATE CONCURRING THEREIN:
13 At the next opportunity whereby Joint Rules of operation are
14 being considered for adoption by the Legislature the following Rule
15 Set shall be considered for adoption:
16 A. The Legislature hereby establishes the Legislative Division
17 of Administrative Code Review, which shall be tasked with reviewing
18 proposed administrative rules of state agencies. The Division shall
19 employ individuals as approved by the Speaker of the Oklahoma House
20 of Representatives and the President Pro Tempore of the State
21 Senate.
22 B. The Division is tasked with evaluating the following:
23 1. Whether proposed permanent administrative rules align with
24 the Oklahoma Constitution;
